_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n38310", "headword_ar": "مدٌّ", "root": "md", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "inf. n. of 1, q. v. ―         -b2-  [As a subst.]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qadoru", "text_ar": "قَدْرُ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mad~i AlbaSari", "text_ar": "مَدِّ البَصَرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  A piece of land (S, L) [occupying]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the space of the extent of vision; i. q."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "madaAhu", "text_ar": "مَدَاهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S, L, K.) It is said in the K, art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mdY", "text_ar": "مدى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", that one should not say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "md~ AlbSr", "text_ar": "مدّ البصر"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", but only"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "madaAhu", "text_ar": "مَدَاهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; this was originally said by El-Hareeree: but some urge against it the expression in a trad.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mad~u", "text_ar": "مَدُّ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Sawoti Almuw^a*~ini", "text_ar": "صَوْتِ المُوَذِّنِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (MF:) the trad. is,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_in~a Almuw^a*~ina", "text_ar": "اـِنَّ المُوَذِّنَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yugofaru lahu mad~a Sawotihi", "text_ar": "يُغْفَرُ لَهُ مَدَّ صَوْتِهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", or, according to another reading,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "madaY Swth", "text_ar": "مَدَى صوته"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; i. e., (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Verily the muëdhdhin shall be forgiven to the extent of the prolonging of his voice;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "meaning,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "largely."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(L, TA.) ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^atayotuhu mad~a", "text_ar": "اَتَيْتُهُ مَدَّ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aln~ahaAri", "text_ar": "النَّهَ